desc: The Crew Yard Cafe & Bistro is a foodies heaven! Open for Breakfast, Lunch & Afternoon Teas, with a full Vegan Menu also available. We also cater for Gluten Free! Our Courtyard is perfect for when the weather is sunny, or keep warm inside when the weather is a rainy! You'll also find thousands of Antiques to browse!

layout.text: From small to large Antiques & Curios
